---
// src/components/JourneyAndPartners.astro
---

<section class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl">
        <!-- Journey Header -->
        <div class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold">
                Our journey reflects
                <span class="bg-[#FFA500] px-2">our steady</span>
            </h2>
            <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold mt-2">
                <span class="bg-[#FFA500] px-2"
                    >growth and unwavering excellence</span
                >
            </h2>
        </div>

        <!-- Subtitle -->
        <p class="text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-12">
            WE ARE MOVING IN FOUR MAIN DIRECTIONS
        </p>

        <!-- Journey Content Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 mb-20">
            <!-- Left Column -->
            <div class="space-y-12">
                <div class="border-t border-b border-gray-200 py-8">
                    <p class="text-gray-700">
                        Dnipropetrovs'k Special Repair Plant Limited Liability
                        Company has been operating since 2003. Over the years,
                        the company has changed its core business areas, but the
                        high quality of its work has remained unchanged. The
                        company has its own production base: skilled workers,
                        machine tools, and crane facilities.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="border-t border-b border-gray-200 py-8">
                    <p class="text-gray-700">
                        The company has its own production base with skilled
                        workers, machine tools, and crane facilities. Over the
                        years, many enterprises know DZS LLC as a reliable
                        partner.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Right Column -->
            <div class="space-y-12">
                <div class="border-t border-b border-gray-200 py-8">
                    <p class="text-gray-700">
                        Over the years, our company has interacted with many
                        enterprises that today know DZS LLC as a reliable
                        partner who can be entrusted with complex and
                        responsible work, an honest customer and employer. The
                        company operates in accordance with the requirements of
                        the Law of Ukraine and is supported by all the necessary
                        documents.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="border-t border-b border-gray-200 py-8">
                    <p class="text-gray-700">
                        To date, DZS LLC has mastered the repair and manufacture
                        of components for planetary gearboxes and custom
                        friction products, like brake pads for Hitachi 3500.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Partners Section -->
        <div class="bg-[#0B1437] py-16 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-center text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-12">
                LOVED BY THE GREATEST COMPANIES AROUND THE WORLD
            </p>

            <!-- Partners Logo Grid -->
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-12 px-4">
                <img
                    src="/partners/elme-messer.png"
                    alt="Elme Messer"
                    class="h-12 object-contain"
                />
                <img
                    src="/partners/cks.png"
                    alt="CKS"
                    class="h-12 object-contain"
                />
                <img
                    src="/partners/ferrexpo.png"
                    alt="Ferrexpo"
                    class="h-12 object-contain"
                />
                <img
                    src="/partners/metinvest.png"
                    alt="Metinvest"
                    class="h-12 object-contain"
                />
                <img
                    src="/partners/neocarb.png"
                    alt="Neocarb"
                    class="h-12 object-contain"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
